name: Analog Journey - Dreamline
description: "Analog Journey is a small collection of simulated chiptunes, made with "Analog" instrument on Ableton. It is the synthesis of my path, my story and my feelings, presented to you in 8 bits. Dreamline is part of "Dad's Breath" Soundtrack. A game made with Suami 'KomBits' Abdalla. For LDJam 43." Created by Pedro Kozovits A.K.A Fractal Vector. Personal, non-commercial use only.
